<div class="callout statute">
  <p style="margin:0"><span class="k">About this page.</span> §82.116 requires the Association to record a management certificate and to make its dedicatory instruments available to members. §82.1142 contemplates a member-accessible website. This page and the <a href="/governing-documents/">Governing Documents</a> page serve that member-accessible function. The recorded certificate on file with Hays County, and the copy on file with the Texas Real Estate Commission, are the official versions.</p>
